  "title": "Contracts Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>Assist the General Manager during the bidding process with activities such as issuing the RFP, receive and analyze the proposals and preparation of the BAW.</li><li>Support the team with all necessary duties to develop and deliver comprehensive design and construction contracts.</li><li>Ensure change management outcomes are captured and reflected within Timberline.</li><li>Provide formal responses to contractual matters.</li><li>Providing support in the tracking, expediting, collecting and collating contractor’s daily, weekly and monthly reports and other regular data submissions.</li><li>Manage bidding process activities ranging from facilitating issuance of the RFP, providing analysis of tender returns and finalise preparation of the BAW.</li><li>Approve payment certificate of supply chain partners.</li><li>All duties are to be performed in accordance with departmental and corporate operating procedures and policies.</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <strong>ram@deshingroup.com; davidnhbsg@gmail.com; wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
